<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">As far as I know, that&apos;s the end. If you discover a sequel, please let me know! But I think L&apos;Amour wanted to leave the story open ended. You kind of <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">As far as I know, that's the end. If you discover a sequel, please let me know! But I think L'Amour wanted to leave the story open ended. You kind of know everyone's plans. You can sort of imagine what will happen in their futures. But you're still left wondering....<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
