              <span id="reviewTextContainer3907743550" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4816630627957063228">Great book, great characters in the story. This I thought was one of the Better Louis L Lamour books I have read lately. Picked this book up on a fluke. There are so many books he has authored. He was really feeling it when he wrote this book. I thought I was reading Robert Wheeler, Or Hemingway. It was that good. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


