              <span id="reviewTextContainer179595158" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11728671846372615891">Bendigo and his brother Cain are part of a wagontrain heading west. When they get to South Pass in Wyoming, they and several others decide to stop and build a town. Bendigo transitions to manhood while dealing with Indians, thieves, and other incidents.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

